PN,16303
SC,0003
CT,20,T
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1781269896
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 26 Jun to Fri 10 Jul
OL,6,FHigh pressure is expected to lie close
OL,7,Fto the UK at the start of this period,
OL,8,Fbringing settled and mainly dry
OL,9,Fconditions. Temperatures will likely
OL,10,Fbe above normal, with potential for
OL,11,Fhot conditions to develop, especially
OL,12,Fin the south. Into July, weakening of
OL,13,Fthe high pressure may bring an
OL,14,Fincreasing chance of more unsettled
OL,15,Fweather and thunderstorms, especially
OL,16,Fin the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
